Song Info 
---------------------
""Waking Up In Vegas is the fourth hit single from the album One Of The Boys. The song has gathered major air-play and sales recently, and is living up to Perry's repetition of HOT HOT songs. Like "I Kissed A Girl" the song has a rock style beat to it but also has features of Hot N Cold and Ur So Gay.

Waking Up In Vegas currently is Katy Perry's most radio friendly song. Listeners agree.

Although previous single, Thinking Of U did poorly compared to Hot N Cold and I Kissed A Girl, Perry is pulling back up with Waking Up In Vegas, which is sure to be a hit."
